{"word":"οὗ","slug":"οὗ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>οὗ</el></b> [the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὅς\">ὅς</a></el>], as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> and question about location<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as introduction to information or activity relative to a place, condition, or document <b>where <a href='B:470 2:9'>Mt 2:9</a>; <a href='B:470 18:20'>18:20</a>; <a href='B:490 4:16'>Lk 4:16f</a>; <a href='B:490 23:53'>23:53</a>; <a href='B:510 1:13'>Ac 1:13</a>; <a href='B:510 2:2'>2:2</a>; <a href='B:510 7:29'>7:29</a>; <a href='B:510 12:12'>12:12</a>; <a href='B:510 16:13'>16:13</a>; <a href='B:510 20:6'>20:6</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>, 8; <a href='B:510 25:10'>25:10</a>; <a href='B:510 28:14'>28:14</a>; <a href='B:520 4:15'>Ro 4:15</a>; <a href='B:520 5:20'>5:20</a>; <a href='B:520 9:26'>9:26</a>; <a href='B:540 3:17'>2 Cor 3:17</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on direction, <b>to which, where, whither, <a href='B:470 28:16'>Mt 28:16</a>; <a href='B:490 10:1'>Lk 10:1</a>; <a href='B:490 24:28'>24:28</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐάν\">ἐάν</a></el> <b><a href='B:530 16:6'>1 Cor 16:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὅτου\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:οὐ/οὐκ/οὐχ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}